My profile:
Risk: [Low/Med/High] | Horizon: [1–3y / 3–5y / 5y+] | Style: [Value/GARP/Growth/Dividend]
Sectors preferred: [ ] | Avoid: [ ] | Market cap: [Large/Mid/Small/Any]
Constraints: [e.g., avoid high debt, avoid biotech, prefer profitable]

Hard filters (must apply):
1. Positive FCF in TTM OR clear path to FCF within 12–18 months (state which)
2. Revenue growth and gross margin trend (3Y + TTM)
