Must include:
1. Guidance: what changed vs last quarter; quantify revisions
2. Drivers: revenue mix, pricing, volumes, churn/NRR, backlog, capacity, etc. (as applicable)
3. Margin drivers: gross margin bridge + opex discipline
4. Competitive mentions: named competitors, pricing pressure, share gains/losses
